WEBVTT

00:21.830 --> 00:23.190
What do you make of

00:24.190 --> 00:25.390
what happened today?

00:25.760 --> 00:27.640
Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu

00:27.800 --> 00:29.830
were targeting Li Lejun from the start.

00:29.830 --> 00:33.110
Li Lejun really did plot
against the Princess.

00:34.110 --> 00:37.150
But Xiao Wuyi and Xie Jiayu
may have framed her

00:37.880 --> 00:38.670
as well.

00:39.310 --> 00:40.600
Your Majesty means

00:40.880 --> 00:42.910
there is a third Phoenix Heart Token—

00:42.910 --> 00:45.110
the one Empress Wenxi once gave Xiao Ju.

00:45.560 --> 00:47.240
Then, where is the Princess's

00:47.390 --> 00:48.790
Phoenix Heart Token now?

00:50.560 --> 00:51.390
Li Mao.

00:52.560 --> 00:53.820
I underestimated him.

00:54.750 --> 00:57.680
Just now, when Li Lejun
was arrested and imprisoned,

00:57.920 --> 00:59.920
he didn't say a word in her defense.

01:00.960 --> 01:01.770
Li Mao.

01:03.070 --> 01:04.480
Xie Jiayu.

01:05.349 --> 01:06.680
Xiao Wuyi.

01:08.230 --> 01:09.230
See?

01:10.760 --> 01:12.620
Things are getting interesting.

02:41.090 --> 02:45.250
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:45.460 --> 02:48.180
[Episode 19]

03:08.520 --> 03:11.380
You came from the lowest ranks
of society yourself.

03:13.190 --> 03:15.150
Since you decided to take this position,

03:15.150 --> 03:16.710
you should have a more compassionate heart

03:16.710 --> 03:18.440
and a greater sense of purpose.

03:28.960 --> 03:30.079
Little beggar.

03:32.400 --> 03:33.360
Come on.

03:39.470 --> 03:40.400
Eat slowly.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.790
Where is your family?

03:44.910 --> 03:45.710
They're dead.

03:48.150 --> 03:49.210
Where are you from?

03:49.360 --> 03:50.120
Qizhou.

03:50.630 --> 03:51.760
Where are you going?

03:51.840 --> 03:52.520
Jiankang.

04:00.640 --> 04:01.450
Who is it?

04:03.430 --> 04:06.310
I am here to bring Your Highness
a calming herbal tonic.

04:06.310 --> 04:07.240
You again.

04:08.430 --> 04:09.760
Still haven't given up?

04:24.920 --> 04:25.950
Then stay.

04:28.160 --> 04:29.620
Thank you, Your Highness.

04:40.750 --> 04:41.680
Smile more.

04:43.680 --> 04:45.740
You look like her only when you smile.

05:00.040 --> 05:00.840
What's wrong?

05:01.400 --> 05:04.380
[Xuanzheng Hall]

05:07.720 --> 05:10.450
Mother never brought me
to the palace in the past.

05:11.270 --> 05:12.950
She said there is nothing fun.

05:15.600 --> 05:17.130
Today is my first time here,

05:17.390 --> 05:19.590
and it's true that there's nothing fun.

05:19.920 --> 05:21.650
I never want to come here again.

05:24.720 --> 05:25.390
Okay.

05:27.560 --> 05:28.430
Then don't.

05:34.159 --> 05:35.950
You just gave Cui Jun's
Phoenix Heart Token

05:35.950 --> 05:37.000
away like that?

05:37.870 --> 05:38.600
Don't worry.

05:39.310 --> 05:40.750
Since I dared to give it away,

05:40.750 --> 05:41.680
I can get it back.

05:42.310 --> 05:44.370
I'll get the Cui family's mine first.

05:45.640 --> 05:46.440
Let's go home.

06:11.830 --> 06:13.310
Not burying Her Highness

06:14.120 --> 06:15.720
until Li Lejun was captured—

06:16.160 --> 06:17.560
was that a promise to her?

06:18.430 --> 06:19.630
Do souls really exist

06:20.920 --> 06:22.360
after death?

06:27.950 --> 06:28.870
She will know.

06:32.040 --> 06:33.300
As long as you believe,

06:34.070 --> 06:34.950
she exists

06:35.750 --> 06:36.560
and will know.

06:38.480 --> 06:39.390
Is this how you

06:40.070 --> 06:41.610
commemorate your parents?

06:46.310 --> 06:47.840
Maybe I shouldn't say that.

06:50.310 --> 06:51.440
I've never met them,

06:51.940 --> 06:53.200
but I get curious, too.

06:53.950 --> 06:55.950
Just like when you listen to a story,

06:56.000 --> 06:57.950
you'd wonder how the person in the story

06:57.950 --> 06:59.159
is related to you.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.270
But in this world,

07:02.070 --> 07:05.200
you can't empathize
without experiencing it yourself.

07:05.560 --> 07:07.490
So I can't say it's commemoration.

07:07.600 --> 07:09.600
The Xiao family gave me everything.

07:09.870 --> 07:11.070
The power in my hands,

07:12.190 --> 07:13.450
the ambition I uphold,

07:14.160 --> 07:15.360
the bonds I hold dear,

07:16.040 --> 07:17.360
and the mission I bear.

07:18.040 --> 07:19.600
Whether glory or disgrace,

07:20.630 --> 07:23.690
none of this has anything
to do with Crown Prince Wenxi.

07:23.720 --> 07:24.950
I am looking for the Phoenix Heart Token

07:24.950 --> 07:26.240
for the minerals behind it,

07:26.240 --> 07:28.000
which can be used to make caltrop fireball

07:28.000 --> 07:28.870
to serve Ye.

07:30.270 --> 07:31.240
The path I chose

07:31.800 --> 07:33.390
was never in the court.

07:35.040 --> 07:36.500
I just want to be Xiao Wuyi.

07:37.630 --> 07:38.310
That night,

07:38.560 --> 07:40.240
you saw me arguing with Her Highness.

07:40.240 --> 07:42.240
That was what we were talking about.

07:42.390 --> 07:44.190
I never wanted to implicate her.

07:44.950 --> 07:46.280
Who says we stand alone?

07:47.000 --> 07:48.240
We share weal and woe.

07:50.310 --> 07:51.190
I see.

07:52.240 --> 07:53.440
No wonder Mother said

07:54.159 --> 07:55.430
you have a good name.

07:58.180 --> 08:00.040
But now the Cui family has fallen,

08:00.310 --> 08:01.830
and Mother has passed away.

08:01.830 --> 08:03.430
Only the Xiao family is left.

08:03.630 --> 08:05.160
You control the Beifu army.

08:05.240 --> 08:07.830
Prince Jing'an's Household will become
even more threatening in their eyes.

08:07.830 --> 08:08.830
Your identity

08:09.680 --> 08:11.740
might not be hidden anymore, either.

08:14.240 --> 08:15.170
It should be them

08:15.920 --> 08:16.830
who are afraid

08:16.830 --> 08:19.360
that I will admit
to being Crown Prince Wenxi.

08:25.440 --> 08:27.130
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

08:28.680 --> 08:29.750
Your Highness!

08:29.750 --> 08:30.920
Auntie Xie!

08:30.920 --> 08:32.030
You're back.

08:32.360 --> 08:35.419
I made Auntie's favorite
wild-green flatbread today.

08:53.080 --> 08:54.680
I'll accept your black iron.

08:55.600 --> 08:56.480
But actually,

08:59.440 --> 09:01.170
there is something I want more.

09:01.270 --> 09:02.240
What do you want?

09:04.150 --> 09:05.030
Your courage.

09:05.720 --> 09:06.510
Courage?

09:09.960 --> 09:12.560
Being kind and soft-hearted
is not your fault.

09:13.910 --> 09:15.360
Don't let past betrayals

09:16.440 --> 09:19.440
make you completely lose
the courage to trust others.

09:22.480 --> 09:24.010
You still have new friends,

09:26.510 --> 09:28.040
and you will have a new home.

09:33.750 --> 09:36.080
Actually, before I went to Lingfeng Fort,

09:37.200 --> 09:39.130
I had never really seen suffering.

09:40.590 --> 09:41.990
I grew up in the Xie family

09:42.000 --> 09:43.400
and was raised by Mother.

09:44.030 --> 09:45.430
I thought I was oppressed

09:45.650 --> 09:48.180
simply because I had no say
in my own marriage.

09:48.200 --> 09:49.530
Only later did I realize

09:49.960 --> 09:50.690
that there is

09:51.790 --> 09:53.720
no true haven of peace

09:54.750 --> 09:56.410
and simplicity in this world.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.630
Master once asked me,

10:01.790 --> 10:03.150
"Where is the martial arts world?

10:03.150 --> 10:05.150
And where are the ends of the earth?"

10:05.790 --> 10:06.600
Now,

10:08.750 --> 10:09.720
I understand.

10:10.800 --> 10:13.260
It's always been like this
in chaotic times.

10:14.080 --> 10:16.940
Beneath the feasts and revelry
lie blood and tears.

10:19.150 --> 10:21.280
It is already difficult to stay alive.

10:23.320 --> 10:23.960
Okay.

10:24.510 --> 10:25.390
I promise you.

10:28.870 --> 10:30.670
I'll still have faith in others.

10:35.720 --> 10:36.720
I also promise you

10:37.960 --> 10:40.090
that I will help you uncover the secret
of the Phoenix Heart Token,

10:40.090 --> 10:42.950
find the connection
between the token and the mine,

10:43.550 --> 10:45.880
and help you create the caltrop fireball.

10:48.550 --> 10:49.720
Do you know what

10:50.630 --> 10:51.760
your promise means?

10:52.720 --> 10:54.180
Kindness is not a mistake.

10:54.450 --> 10:59.610
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

10:55.790 --> 10:57.320
But kindness without power

10:58.030 --> 10:59.560
is no better than weakness.

11:00.440 --> 11:04.120
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

11:00.960 --> 11:02.620
This applies to individuals,

11:03.030 --> 11:05.150
and it applies to nations as well.

11:04.150 --> 11:08.350
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

11:06.600 --> 11:07.720
Ye needs Beifu,

11:08.200 --> 11:09.550
otherwise peace is just empty talk.

11:08.460 --> 11:10.930
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

11:10.550 --> 11:12.080
And Beifu needs the caltrop fireball

11:10.960 --> 11:13.940
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

11:12.600 --> 11:14.720
to deter enemies or noble families,

11:13.960 --> 11:17.710
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

11:16.510 --> 11:17.360
even

11:17.740 --> 11:20.430
♪ I shall never forget ♪

11:18.360 --> 11:20.720
it may bring uncontrollable energy.

11:20.520 --> 11:24.900
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

11:22.910 --> 11:24.440
Words alone are not enough.

11:24.670 --> 11:26.080
So let's deter them with power.

11:24.930 --> 11:28.360
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

11:27.870 --> 11:28.670
Xiao Wuyi.

11:28.380 --> 11:31.170
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

11:30.720 --> 11:32.440
Let me be your strongest support.

11:31.190 --> 11:34.190
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

11:34.150 --> 11:35.200
You and me—

11:34.210 --> 11:38.270
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

11:37.750 --> 11:38.510
Let's go together.

11:38.290 --> 11:41.780
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

11:41.800 --> 11:44.720
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

11:44.750 --> 11:50.270
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

11:55.240 --> 11:59.290
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

11:59.430 --> 12:02.920
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

12:02.940 --> 12:05.860
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

12:05.890 --> 12:11.420
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

12:39.960 --> 12:40.760
What's wrong?

12:41.000 --> 12:42.720
You walking in here without saying a word

12:42.720 --> 12:44.000
is scarier than when you stumble in

12:44.000 --> 12:45.030
covered in blood.

12:46.550 --> 12:49.200
You said before
that the blood stasis in my brain

12:49.200 --> 12:50.660
would affect my lifespan.

12:52.240 --> 12:53.750
You'll go blind in two or three years,

12:53.750 --> 12:56.080
and you'll die within three to five years.

13:01.910 --> 13:03.480
Can you help me live longer?

13:07.360 --> 13:08.440
Didn't you say

13:08.870 --> 13:10.600
three to five years was enough?

13:11.360 --> 13:13.560
Why do you suddenly want to live longer?

13:13.810 --> 13:14.870
Can you or not?

13:23.390 --> 13:24.270
Yes,

13:25.030 --> 13:26.490
as long as you listen to me.

13:32.270 --> 13:33.550
If it's a key,

13:33.840 --> 13:35.390
what does it unlock?

13:35.820 --> 13:38.550
It would still require
all 4 pieces put together.

13:40.320 --> 13:42.000
Cui Jun only had one piece

13:42.480 --> 13:44.360
and found one of the mines.

13:46.440 --> 13:47.840
This means it's not a key,

13:48.160 --> 13:49.400
but the totem itself.

13:50.240 --> 13:53.000
The Phoenix Imperial Seal was reforged
into the form of the Vermilion Bird,

13:53.000 --> 13:54.630
with its head and tail
forming a complete whole.

13:54.630 --> 13:56.630
What secret lies within this totem?

13:58.480 --> 13:59.390
Yuanji?

14:03.000 --> 14:04.270
I'm really seeing things.

14:04.270 --> 14:05.600
How could it be Yuanji?

14:08.160 --> 14:08.710
My Lady,

14:09.320 --> 14:10.720
drink it while it's warm.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.080
It clears heat and improves vision.

14:12.080 --> 14:14.080
I just got these herbs from Qing Long.

14:14.080 --> 14:15.200
From Qing Long?

14:15.960 --> 14:17.030
What's wrong with his eyes?

14:17.030 --> 14:19.030
It's because of Cui Jun's kidnapping.

14:19.030 --> 14:20.870
Qing Long was in charge
of keeping the key.

14:20.870 --> 14:22.550
He said the key was never lost.

14:23.080 --> 14:24.240
Even when sleeping,

14:24.280 --> 14:25.510
he kept it close to him.

14:25.510 --> 14:26.480
But the lock

14:26.480 --> 14:28.080
had no signs of being pried.

14:28.790 --> 14:30.480
Qing Long said that unless he was blind,

14:30.480 --> 14:33.140
it couldn't have happened
without him knowing.

14:33.670 --> 14:34.550
Yuanji.

14:35.290 --> 14:37.320
What's wrong with the Heir's Consort?

14:37.320 --> 14:39.150
She is the Empress Dowager's niece.

14:39.150 --> 14:41.740
Why are you saying
such strange things, My Lady?

14:41.740 --> 14:42.740
Of course, she

14:42.760 --> 14:44.560
is the Empress Dowager's niece.

14:46.550 --> 14:47.150
No.

14:47.270 --> 14:48.870
That's not right, Xie Jiayu.

14:48.870 --> 14:50.270
How could you think that?

14:51.120 --> 14:52.580
Yuanji treats you so well.

14:53.390 --> 14:54.360
How could she?

15:06.200 --> 15:08.400
I told you I'm already thinking of a way.

15:08.840 --> 15:11.000
Her Majesty misses her sister.

15:11.440 --> 15:13.420
[He Yuanji's Father]
[He Yuanji's Mother]

15:11.510 --> 15:13.510
She invites your mother
to the palace for a chat.

15:13.510 --> 15:15.040
She'll be back in a few days.

15:15.470 --> 15:18.160
I just came to inform Your Highness.

15:19.600 --> 15:21.080
The Empress Dowager has gone too far.

15:21.080 --> 15:21.960
Over the years,

15:21.960 --> 15:24.030
Her Majesty let you stay
at Prince Jing'an's Mansion

15:24.030 --> 15:25.270
without doing anything,

15:25.270 --> 15:27.360
only to deliver a fatal blow today.

15:27.790 --> 15:28.790
No matter what,

15:28.790 --> 15:30.590
you are a member of the He family.

15:30.960 --> 15:33.200
The lives of hundreds
of people in your family

15:33.200 --> 15:34.840
are in Her Majesty's hands.

15:35.360 --> 15:37.030
You'd better weigh your options carefully.

15:37.030 --> 15:38.910
I already helped
Her Majesty kidnap Cui Jun.

15:38.910 --> 15:40.480
How can I get the Phoenix Heart Token now?

15:40.480 --> 15:42.010
You figure it out yourself.

15:42.200 --> 15:43.550
I heard Your Highness

15:43.550 --> 15:45.970
has been visiting
Zhengtong Bookstore frequently lately.

15:45.970 --> 15:47.790
Is there someone there who reminds you
of an old acquaintance,

15:47.790 --> 15:50.030
someone you still hold dear?

15:50.240 --> 15:52.360
If you refuse to find a way,

15:52.600 --> 15:55.480
Her Majesty will find one herself.

16:00.790 --> 16:01.840
The place where Cui Jun was held

16:01.840 --> 16:03.650
was His Highness's
hidden house in Jiankang.

16:03.650 --> 16:04.390
No one could escape from there,

16:04.390 --> 16:05.550
and no one even knows it exists.

16:05.550 --> 16:06.510
Cui Jun lost a hand,

16:06.510 --> 16:07.840
yet he vanished into thin air.

16:07.840 --> 16:08.910
It's like something out of a ghost story.

16:08.910 --> 16:09.600
There is only one key

16:09.600 --> 16:10.670
to the hidden house in the world,

16:10.670 --> 16:12.480
and His Highness entrusted it to me.

16:12.480 --> 16:13.540
I swear upon Heaven

16:13.630 --> 16:14.670
that I never leaked the key,

16:14.670 --> 16:16.270
nor did I help Cui Jun escape.

16:18.200 --> 16:19.120
On the day of the palace banquet,

16:19.120 --> 16:21.550
His Highness traded the Phoenix Heart Token
for the Cui family's mines.

16:21.550 --> 16:22.960
The noble families didn't get a share.

16:22.960 --> 16:24.150
They thought they had suffered a loss,

16:24.150 --> 16:25.870
so they joined forces
to accuse His Highness,

16:25.870 --> 16:28.230
saying his reform
of Beifu was for himself.

16:28.230 --> 16:29.320
These old geezers

16:29.790 --> 16:31.200
are clearly making a fuss over nothing

16:31.200 --> 16:32.460
to frame His Highness.

16:32.960 --> 16:34.000
He really didn't do it himself?

16:34.000 --> 16:35.000
Oh, Lady Xie.

16:35.000 --> 16:35.790
Alright.

16:35.960 --> 16:36.750
Calm down.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.770
I believe it wasn't him.

16:39.440 --> 16:41.630
But it's indeed quite suspicious.

16:42.080 --> 16:43.200
Hiding the person on purpose

16:43.200 --> 16:44.600
to see how everyone reacts.

16:44.600 --> 16:47.510
Would you call this a feint
or taking advantage of the chaos

16:47.510 --> 16:48.750
in military strategy?

16:48.750 --> 16:50.000
Not this time.

16:51.030 --> 16:51.840
Then Xiao Wuyi

16:52.000 --> 16:53.600
just going to let them frame him?

16:53.600 --> 16:55.270
Hasn't His Highness always been like this?

16:55.270 --> 16:57.510
He never cares what others say or think.

17:04.920 --> 17:05.480
My Lady,

17:06.109 --> 17:08.770
the Heir's Consort
is indeed not in the mansion.

17:11.160 --> 17:13.290
Outsiders had no chance to get near it,

17:13.589 --> 17:15.450
but what if it was someone inside?

17:21.310 --> 17:21.829
Anmin.

17:23.880 --> 17:25.680
You went to the bookstore again?

17:26.200 --> 17:27.589
I found another

17:27.589 --> 17:29.260
extremely precious ancient book today.

17:29.260 --> 17:29.820
Right,

17:30.000 --> 17:32.200
I also found some ancient books
on canal building.

17:32.200 --> 17:34.070
They were left by craftsmen
who followed Li Luhai

17:34.070 --> 17:35.920
when they built the Qin Canal in the past.

17:35.920 --> 17:37.350
You currently hold

17:37.350 --> 17:39.400
the position overseeing the construction
of the new canal.

17:39.400 --> 17:41.070
These books

17:41.070 --> 17:42.070
might also be very important to you.

17:42.070 --> 17:44.130
I'll have them copied and sent to you.

17:44.240 --> 17:46.300
I didn't expect you to keep it in mind.

17:46.750 --> 17:48.790
But it's chaotic outside these few days.

17:48.790 --> 17:50.050
You should go out less.

17:53.440 --> 17:53.960
Got it.

17:55.750 --> 17:56.350
Yuanji.

17:58.200 --> 17:59.530
Is there anything else?

18:02.160 --> 18:04.490
Bring more people
with you when you go out.

18:04.510 --> 18:05.030
Okay.

18:25.310 --> 18:26.840
I'm not playing Go with you.

18:27.270 --> 18:28.830
You're even worse at Go than Father.

18:28.830 --> 18:29.760
I'm in a bad mood.

18:29.880 --> 18:30.940
Play a game with me.

18:32.110 --> 18:33.510
Rather than spending your time here,

18:33.510 --> 18:35.480
why don't you just be honest with her?

18:35.480 --> 18:36.640
It's been five years.

18:36.640 --> 18:37.920
Anmin, you really know
how to drag things out.

18:37.920 --> 18:38.400
You—

18:39.270 --> 18:39.920
Xiao Wuyi.

18:40.610 --> 18:41.830
She is your Consort.

18:42.790 --> 18:45.320
You never care
about having a bad reputation,

18:45.660 --> 18:47.010
but she's a woman.

18:47.830 --> 18:48.830
Can she not care?

18:49.510 --> 18:50.400
If I tell her,

18:51.240 --> 18:53.440
how can she gain a foothold
in Jiankang?

18:53.720 --> 18:55.410
She is not as pedantic as you.

18:55.740 --> 18:56.260
You.

19:00.440 --> 19:01.170
What is this?

19:06.750 --> 19:09.080
I've already given her the divorce paper.

19:09.080 --> 19:10.240
She is free now.

19:11.480 --> 19:13.000
Don't blame me for not reminding you.

19:13.000 --> 19:14.120
If you don't make a move soon,

19:14.120 --> 19:15.180
they might rekindle their old flame,

19:15.180 --> 19:16.990
and you'll regret it when it's too late.

19:16.990 --> 19:18.430
Liu Zhaolin is really...

19:37.160 --> 19:38.910
The Heir's Consort has gone out again?

19:38.910 --> 19:40.200
Yes, she just left.

19:40.950 --> 19:43.610
Quick, take off your clothes
and give them to me.

19:44.400 --> 19:45.200
The old rules.

19:45.310 --> 19:46.910
Do exactly as you did before.

19:47.480 --> 19:48.610
No matter who comes later,

19:48.610 --> 19:49.810
just pretend to be me.

19:54.170 --> 19:55.990
[Zhengtong Bookstore]

19:54.480 --> 19:55.960
I didn't expect Your Highness

19:55.960 --> 19:57.640
to have such insight and literary talent.

19:57.640 --> 19:58.500
I am impressed.

19:58.790 --> 19:59.920
You flatter me, sir.

20:00.350 --> 20:01.070
Thanks to

20:01.070 --> 20:03.130
the books you copied for me last time,

20:03.400 --> 20:04.590
I benefited a lot.

20:05.310 --> 20:07.480
But I still have a few doubts here.

20:07.790 --> 20:09.590
I hope you can explain them to me.

20:10.680 --> 20:11.610
Confucius said,

20:11.790 --> 20:15.000
"Zilu, do you understand
what true knowledge is?

20:15.880 --> 20:17.590
To know what you know, and admit

20:17.590 --> 20:19.070
what you do not know—

20:19.920 --> 20:21.120
that is true wisdom."

20:37.350 --> 20:39.880
Have you ever been to Yingzhou?

20:41.660 --> 20:42.350
No.

20:43.340 --> 20:45.050
Why the question?

20:46.790 --> 20:49.510
It's just that you look

20:49.960 --> 20:51.620
exactly like a friend of mine.

20:52.030 --> 20:53.310
He was from Yingzhou.

20:54.550 --> 20:56.240
Is it Mr. Pei?

20:56.430 --> 20:57.260
Yes.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.200
He has passed away.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.240
I see.

21:04.200 --> 21:06.720
The Pei family in Yingzhou
is a prominent family.

21:06.720 --> 21:09.680
Young Master Pei must also come
from a prestigious family

21:09.680 --> 21:10.790
and be a man of extraordinary talent.

21:10.790 --> 21:11.960
I am just a commoner,

21:12.950 --> 21:15.010
and dare not compare myself with him.

21:42.640 --> 21:44.960
Yuanji is meeting her lover here?

21:45.670 --> 21:46.800
Sorry to interrupt.

21:52.680 --> 21:53.210
Nanxing?

21:54.350 --> 21:56.240
Your Highness, My Lady is missing.

21:56.240 --> 21:56.920
She suspects

21:56.920 --> 21:58.920
that the Heir's Consort might be involved
in Cui Jun's disappearance.

21:58.920 --> 22:00.030
Today, when the Heir's Consort went out,

22:00.030 --> 22:01.270
she followed her.

22:02.040 --> 22:03.570
I knew it was related to her.

22:03.750 --> 22:05.150
Why did she get involved?

22:05.420 --> 22:07.200
Your Highness, you really knew it?

22:07.200 --> 22:08.460
I didn't know you knew.

22:08.590 --> 22:09.850
When Lady Xie asked me,

22:09.920 --> 22:12.830
I even said with absolute certainty
that you didn't know.

22:12.830 --> 22:13.440
At 5 p.m.,

22:13.440 --> 22:14.880
the Heir's Consort had already returned.

22:14.880 --> 22:16.500
But My Lady hasn't returned yet.

22:16.500 --> 22:17.350
Where are the Shadow Envoys?

22:17.350 --> 22:19.790
My Lady found a way to unlock the secret
of the Phoenix Heart Token.

22:19.790 --> 22:21.290
But she needs the Shadow Envoys
to leave the city to confirm it.

22:21.290 --> 22:22.630
The ones who should be here are absent.

22:22.630 --> 22:25.630
And the ones who shouldn't be here
are running around.

22:38.400 --> 22:40.400
If you want to see Xie Jiayu alive,

22:40.730 --> 22:43.460
bring all the Phoenix Heart Tokens
to Antai Gate.

22:57.440 --> 22:58.300
My little lady,

22:59.400 --> 23:00.600
you've been drugged.

23:01.640 --> 23:02.790
Don't waste your energy.

23:02.790 --> 23:04.640
Cui Jun, why did you kidnap me?

23:10.030 --> 23:11.200
I once had an eagle

23:11.270 --> 23:12.070
named Mingdi.

23:14.350 --> 23:16.950
I found it
when I was tending the herd as a child.

23:17.030 --> 23:18.640
It was shot by a hunter

23:19.310 --> 23:20.270
and was dying.

23:21.240 --> 23:22.310
I saved it.

23:22.590 --> 23:24.510
Since then, it has always been with me.

23:24.510 --> 23:25.750
But since I came to Southern Ye,

23:25.750 --> 23:26.810
it's been 20 years.

23:27.310 --> 23:28.750
I've never seen it again.

23:30.270 --> 23:31.590
It must be dead.

23:32.030 --> 23:33.200
Or it was caught by someone,

23:33.200 --> 23:34.260
cooked, and eaten.

23:34.790 --> 23:35.590
Or its feathers were

23:35.590 --> 23:36.590
plucked one by one

23:36.660 --> 23:37.490
to make a fan.

23:42.680 --> 23:43.480
Don't bother.

23:46.920 --> 23:47.720
Stop!

23:48.310 --> 23:49.510
Take one more step,

23:49.630 --> 23:51.230
and this little girl is dead.

23:51.270 --> 23:51.880
Jiayu!

23:51.960 --> 23:52.510
Cui Jun,

23:52.880 --> 23:53.640
let her go.

23:53.640 --> 23:55.040
Xie Jiayu is just a woman.

23:55.440 --> 23:56.550
Whatever happens

23:56.820 --> 23:58.070
has nothing to do with her.

23:58.070 --> 24:00.720
How could the woman cherished
by both His Highness and the Regent

24:00.720 --> 24:02.320
have nothing to do with this?

24:02.350 --> 24:03.790
Put your weapons down!

24:18.030 --> 24:19.830
You brought the Phoenix Heart Token,
right?

24:19.830 --> 24:20.790
Of course.

24:22.830 --> 24:23.550
Cui Jun,

24:23.760 --> 24:25.070
even if you get the tokens,

24:25.070 --> 24:26.510
you won't be able to escape.

24:26.510 --> 24:27.770
Who said I'm escaping?

24:29.240 --> 24:29.920
Xiao Wuyi,

24:30.310 --> 24:31.720
you and Xie Jiayu put on

24:31.720 --> 24:32.720
a good show.

24:33.000 --> 24:35.070
The token used to frame Li Lejun

24:35.350 --> 24:37.280
belongs to the Xiao family, right?

24:37.680 --> 24:39.080
And Her Highness's token

24:39.350 --> 24:40.920
is still in Li Mao's hands.

24:41.270 --> 24:41.930
It's yours.

24:46.550 --> 24:47.880
As long as you let her go,

24:48.160 --> 24:50.110
I will trade my life for hers.

24:51.750 --> 24:54.510
It seems Prince Qi really cares for you.

24:55.400 --> 24:56.860
He didn't hesitate at all.

24:57.440 --> 24:58.200
Xiao Wuyi,

24:59.030 --> 25:00.030
what about yours?

25:02.110 --> 25:03.970
I do have the Phoenix Heart Token.

25:05.270 --> 25:07.070
But what if I don't give it to you?

25:08.750 --> 25:09.480
Little girl.

25:10.650 --> 25:12.110
Prince Qi is a good choice.

25:13.110 --> 25:14.240
Xiao Wuyi is no good.

25:14.270 --> 25:15.310
In his eyes,

25:15.910 --> 25:17.570
you're not even worth a token.

25:17.750 --> 25:18.350
Wuyi.

25:19.240 --> 25:20.500
Yaoyao is in his hands.

25:20.590 --> 25:24.030
Whoever you choose to die today will die.

25:24.670 --> 25:25.590
I won't choose.

25:25.640 --> 25:26.400
Choose one.

25:26.920 --> 25:30.050
One is willing to give up the
Phoenix Heart Token for you.

25:30.920 --> 25:33.120
The other doesn't care about you at all.

25:35.510 --> 25:36.110
Xiao Wuyi.

25:36.420 --> 25:36.900
I...

25:37.270 --> 25:38.110
Let me go!

25:39.000 --> 25:39.720
Jiayu.

25:41.030 --> 25:41.880
Make a choice.

25:43.070 --> 25:44.270
No one will blame you.

25:59.400 --> 26:00.310
Ashina Qi.

26:03.240 --> 26:04.830
Why make things difficult for her?

26:04.830 --> 26:07.110
I will naturally give you
the Phoenix Heart Token.

26:07.110 --> 26:09.580
You used the Phoenix Heart Token
to drive a wedge

26:09.580 --> 26:11.770
between the court and its ministers.

26:13.680 --> 26:15.080
Since that's the case...

26:19.220 --> 26:20.400
Xiao Wuyi, stop!

26:20.430 --> 26:21.630
I will choose for you!

26:22.480 --> 26:23.310
I will take...

26:24.510 --> 26:25.510
Prince Qi's life.

26:25.680 --> 26:26.270
Good.

26:26.830 --> 26:27.830
If you kill him,

26:28.070 --> 26:29.670
I'll let this little girl go.

26:30.350 --> 26:30.950
Prince Qi,

26:31.400 --> 26:32.240
didn't you say

26:32.440 --> 26:34.840
you're willing
to trade your life for hers?

26:35.010 --> 26:36.280
I'll grant your wish.

26:36.310 --> 26:37.640
Xiao Wuyi, stop!

26:37.680 --> 26:40.310
Xiao Wuyi, I knew
I was right about you.

26:40.960 --> 26:44.020
You really have no respect
for the ruler or your father!

26:44.270 --> 26:45.000
Xiao Wuyi!

26:45.510 --> 26:46.910
He is the current Regent.

26:47.000 --> 26:48.240
This is the Antai Gate.

26:48.240 --> 26:49.530
Are you trying to rebel?

26:49.530 --> 26:50.450
Stop talking.

26:50.830 --> 26:52.440
If Xiao Wuyi really wants to rebel,

26:52.440 --> 26:54.070
are you going to fight him to the death?

26:54.070 --> 26:55.000
Xiao Wuyi,

26:55.640 --> 26:56.960
if you dare to shoot,

26:57.060 --> 26:58.770
it will be an act of regicide.

27:39.680 --> 27:40.310
Tell me,

27:40.550 --> 27:41.610
who kidnapped you?

27:52.440 --> 27:53.400
Mingdi.

27:56.200 --> 27:57.710
It has always been here.

28:02.030 --> 28:04.160
It's here to take me home.

28:08.000 --> 28:09.070
Mingdi.

28:09.960 --> 28:11.720
My Mingdi.

28:27.160 --> 28:28.000
Xiao Wuyi

28:28.270 --> 28:30.930
still didn't bring out
the Phoenix Heart Token.

28:32.480 --> 28:35.480
Li Mao is still not as calm
and steady as Xiao Wuyi.

28:36.110 --> 28:38.830
That arrow aimed at Prince Qi
was always meant to be fired.

28:38.830 --> 28:41.000
Now, everyone in the court

28:41.000 --> 28:43.260
saw Xiao Wuyi shoot an arrow at Prince Qi.

28:43.920 --> 28:45.350
Such disloyalty and treason...

28:45.350 --> 28:47.070
what a pleasant surprise.

28:47.480 --> 28:49.480
Your Majesty, by releasing Cui Jun,

28:49.830 --> 28:51.270
you have achieved two goals at once.

28:51.270 --> 28:52.070
It's truly brilliant.

28:52.070 --> 28:53.130
Really brilliant.

28:53.640 --> 28:54.720
Her Majesty

28:55.270 --> 28:57.310
doesn't want to keep dragging this out
with you

28:57.310 --> 28:59.440
and is willing to give you two ways out.

28:59.440 --> 29:00.480
One,

29:01.240 --> 29:02.510
die right now.

29:03.310 --> 29:04.400
The other,

29:05.000 --> 29:06.200
let you out.

29:06.200 --> 29:07.270
Out?

29:08.070 --> 29:09.930
As a secret agent of Northern Qin,

29:10.310 --> 29:11.510
you've done so much.

29:12.920 --> 29:15.510
You just want to see Ye in chaos, right?

29:16.200 --> 29:19.830
Now, Her Majesty is willing
to give you this chance.

29:25.750 --> 29:26.550
Your Majesty,

29:27.110 --> 29:30.200
are you still going to get rid
of Prince Qi?

29:31.030 --> 29:31.720
I think

29:32.420 --> 29:33.950
it's better to win him over.

29:35.510 --> 29:39.110
Look at Li Lejun. She used to pretend
to be so obedient and harmless.

29:39.110 --> 29:39.920
And now?

29:40.480 --> 29:42.350
Whether it's Li Mao or Li Lejun,

29:42.750 --> 29:45.480
they are nothing but wolves
in sheep's clothing.

29:45.550 --> 29:47.310
It's fine that they have yet
to fully spread their wings.

29:47.310 --> 29:48.590
But, if the day comes

29:48.750 --> 29:50.110
when Li Mao uses the Beifu Reform

29:50.110 --> 29:51.510
to establish his own authority,

29:51.510 --> 29:53.240
where would you and His Majesty

29:53.270 --> 29:54.720
stand?

29:58.880 --> 29:59.830
Young Lord Xiao,

29:58.960 --> 30:03.120
[Ziji Palace]

30:00.110 --> 30:01.960
Her Majesty is angry.

30:02.960 --> 30:06.220
Not only because
you pointed your arrow at Prince Qi today,

30:06.310 --> 30:08.000
breaking the rules of a subject,

30:08.000 --> 30:10.070
but also because you and Lady Xie

30:10.350 --> 30:11.750
committed the crime
of deceiving the throne.

30:11.750 --> 30:12.920
How is this deceiving the throne?

30:12.920 --> 30:13.750
Lady Xie,

30:14.400 --> 30:16.070
His Highness Prince Qi
has already handed over

30:16.070 --> 30:17.640
the third Phoenix Heart Token.

30:17.640 --> 30:18.510
His token

30:18.510 --> 30:20.840
is the one Li Lejun took
from Her Highness.

30:21.270 --> 30:24.350
Then where did the Phoenix Heart Token
that appeared

30:24.350 --> 30:26.150
at the palace banquet come from?

30:26.480 --> 30:29.540
You and Young Lord Xiao, in order
to catch the murderer,

30:29.560 --> 30:31.380
even dared to use Her Majesty
as part of your plan.

30:31.380 --> 30:33.520
Isn't this deceiving the throne?

30:34.550 --> 30:35.480
Xiao Wuyi,

30:36.830 --> 30:37.960
do you plead guilty?

30:39.510 --> 30:40.310
Your Majesty,

30:40.550 --> 30:41.830
the Phoenix Heart Token from that day

30:41.830 --> 30:43.790
was indeed granted
by Empress Wenxi to my father

30:43.790 --> 30:44.990
and passed down to me.

30:45.550 --> 30:46.810
To catch the murderer,

30:47.030 --> 30:48.160
I used Your Majesty.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.370
I plead guilty.

30:51.480 --> 30:53.230
But Xie Jiayu was only acting out
of concern for her mother.

30:53.230 --> 30:54.230
She meant no harm.

30:54.720 --> 30:58.050
And the injustice she presented
was not a false accusation.

30:58.680 --> 31:00.160
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

31:00.160 --> 31:02.510
I am willing to take the punishment
for Lady Xie as well.

31:02.510 --> 31:04.070
Such devotion.

31:04.510 --> 31:06.040
Then I will grant your wish.

31:07.110 --> 31:08.240
You shall

31:08.480 --> 31:09.940
take her flogging as well.

31:10.400 --> 31:11.800
Thank you, Your Majesty.

31:17.770 --> 31:19.100
No, I plead guilty, too.

31:19.680 --> 31:20.740
Let's split it half and half.

31:20.740 --> 31:23.400
You shouldn't
take the beating all by yourself.

31:35.720 --> 31:36.310
Start it.

31:37.680 --> 31:38.940
Begin the punishment.

32:02.270 --> 32:02.960
Xiao Wuyi!

32:06.680 --> 32:07.640
Lady Xie,

32:07.920 --> 32:09.080
if you stop it,

32:09.110 --> 32:10.880
it will not only be deceiving the throne

32:10.880 --> 32:12.940
but also defying an imperial decree.

32:15.960 --> 32:16.560
Continue.

32:17.160 --> 32:18.440
Xiao Wuyi!

32:20.160 --> 32:20.830
No!

32:23.960 --> 32:25.400
No!

32:29.110 --> 32:31.110
Do you understand what it means
to be ruler and subject?

32:31.110 --> 32:32.350
You were born to be a ruler.

32:32.350 --> 32:34.680
If you refuse to become Crown Prince Wenxi

32:34.680 --> 32:36.590
and sit on that throne in Jiankang Palace,

32:36.590 --> 32:38.000
choosing instead
to remain a subject for life

32:38.000 --> 32:39.510
even with Beifu Army in your hands,

32:39.510 --> 32:41.160
you will still be feared and restrained
by others all your life.

32:41.160 --> 32:42.880
Your every move will be constrained.

32:42.880 --> 32:44.070
If I sit on that throne,

32:44.070 --> 32:45.870
will I be free from constraints?

32:47.070 --> 32:48.300
With the noble families
controlling the military,

32:48.300 --> 32:49.680
whoever sits in that position

32:49.680 --> 32:51.070
will inevitably be constrained.

32:51.070 --> 32:52.870
That's why I established Beifu,

32:53.240 --> 32:55.830
an army that doesn't belong
to the noble families.

32:55.830 --> 32:56.920
I want countless common-born talents

32:56.920 --> 32:58.880
to have the chance to make their mark
and find a place in this world.

32:58.880 --> 32:59.590
Even if the noble families

32:59.590 --> 33:01.320
can never truly be suppressed,

33:01.370 --> 33:02.830
I still want to bring fresh blood

33:02.830 --> 33:03.760
into Ye's court.

33:06.830 --> 33:08.690
There are many things I need to do,

33:10.790 --> 33:12.520
but I don't have much time left.

33:12.880 --> 33:13.810
What do you mean?

33:14.510 --> 33:16.480
I was injured at Jiuzhang Plain,

33:16.920 --> 33:18.720
and my lifespan is compromised.

33:21.590 --> 33:23.390
Heaven didn't give me more time.

33:28.270 --> 33:30.530
Heaven's will abandoned me 25 years ago.

33:31.240 --> 33:32.900
What I seek is not that throne.

33:34.540 --> 33:35.480
If I don't want the Beifu Army

33:35.480 --> 33:37.010
to disappear with my death,

33:37.720 --> 33:39.110
I must do more things,

33:39.750 --> 33:42.410
rather than merely sitting
above everyone else

33:42.750 --> 33:45.080
and negotiating with the noble families.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.310
You trust Prince Qi

33:49.350 --> 33:51.080
and are willing to support him?

33:51.880 --> 33:53.680
Perhaps as Xie Jiayu's husband,

33:54.510 --> 33:56.770
he is not satisfactory to Your Highness.

33:58.070 --> 33:59.530
But I know he has ambition.

34:02.070 --> 34:03.030
What if one day

34:04.400 --> 34:06.130
you find he doesn't deserve it?

34:27.440 --> 34:28.760
In your future actions,

34:28.760 --> 34:31.219
can you spare a little thought
for yourself?

34:31.480 --> 34:32.150
Today,

34:32.360 --> 34:33.070
you actually aimed your bow

34:33.070 --> 34:34.360
at Mao in public.

34:36.030 --> 34:37.489
Are you worried about Mao?

34:37.510 --> 34:38.880
I'm not joking with you.

34:39.710 --> 34:40.590
Neither am I.

34:54.030 --> 34:54.880
In the past,

34:55.590 --> 34:57.400
I heard many rumors about you.

34:58.110 --> 34:59.280
Because of them,

35:00.400 --> 35:03.230
I was very afraid of you
and doubted you

35:03.880 --> 35:05.740
when I first entered the mansion.

35:07.550 --> 35:09.070
If it weren't for the fact that

35:09.070 --> 35:11.190
we've been through so many things
together later,

35:11.190 --> 35:13.590
I wouldn't have gotten to know
the real you.

35:14.840 --> 35:15.900
And I wouldn't have

35:19.670 --> 35:21.230
fallen for you.

35:32.070 --> 35:33.000
What did you say?

35:38.880 --> 35:39.590
I mean,

35:49.000 --> 35:49.760
Xiao Wuyi,

35:53.190 --> 35:54.670
I'm in love with you.

36:05.030 --> 36:07.190
If we are merely traveling the same road,

36:07.190 --> 36:09.720
when our paths diverge, we must part ways.

36:11.880 --> 36:12.550
Xiao Wuyi,

36:14.710 --> 36:17.170
I don't just want
to walk the same path as you.

36:17.800 --> 36:18.840
I want to walk it

36:19.590 --> 36:20.920
to the very end with you.

36:28.070 --> 36:29.510
So from now on,

36:30.000 --> 36:32.660
could you please think
about yourself a little?

36:33.190 --> 36:34.850
If you have a good reputation,

36:35.000 --> 36:36.710
even if you make mistakes in the future,

36:36.710 --> 36:38.150
people will still believe you.

36:38.150 --> 36:40.610
Wouldn't it be easier
to achieve your goals?

36:44.230 --> 36:47.160
Look how good the Grand Tutor
is at deceiving people.

36:48.880 --> 36:50.480
Everyone says you are smart,

36:50.710 --> 36:52.570
but why do I think you are foolish?

36:54.760 --> 36:55.880
In the court,

36:56.760 --> 36:58.490
someone must play the villain,

36:58.880 --> 37:00.740
and someone must play the savior.

37:01.670 --> 37:04.470
I've already chosen someone
to play the good side.

37:05.050 --> 37:06.910
I don't mind playing the villain.

37:07.150 --> 37:09.610
Have you ever thought
about your own ending?

37:11.720 --> 37:13.450
Although I don't like reading,

37:13.770 --> 37:15.300
I've read many storybooks.

37:16.110 --> 37:17.920
Throughout history, subjects

37:18.800 --> 37:21.730
who love playing the villain like you
never end well.

37:26.480 --> 37:27.110
Yes.

37:29.480 --> 37:31.740
So I dare not expect to keep you
by my side.

37:35.230 --> 37:36.760
What if I insist?

37:39.630 --> 37:40.480
Can you

37:42.640 --> 37:44.300
take better care of yourself?

37:52.320 --> 37:54.520
You told me to treat this place
as my home

37:54.760 --> 37:56.760
and promised Mother
to keep me safe.

37:57.550 --> 37:59.350
But I know what you're thinking.

38:00.000 --> 38:02.660
You would simply arrange
a hundred or so guards,

38:03.590 --> 38:06.920
and if something happened
to you or the Xiao family in the future,

38:06.920 --> 38:09.010
they would escort me away. Am I right?

38:11.330 --> 38:13.330
I don't want to rely on you like this.

38:20.110 --> 38:21.310
Then what do you want?

38:27.350 --> 38:30.190
What if I don't want
to be the wife of the infamous Demon Xiao,

38:30.190 --> 38:31.550
but the wife of a hero?

38:37.390 --> 38:38.430
I want you

38:41.270 --> 38:42.400
to live a long life,

38:43.390 --> 38:44.470
to live in peace,

38:47.250 --> 38:49.110
